{"tid":1228774,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"［圖文教學］致義士：極簡易紙巾花教學","createTime":"2019-06-15T18:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:38:17.000Z","uid":138060,"like":109,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"674067cd2314e3b47edebaa4ed3fbf882949cb87","tid":1228774,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:06:59.000Z","msg":"訓唔到，發夢做少少嘢，歡迎廣傳，希望大家發夢時整多啲。<br />\n如果聽日一路夢遊一路整都唔錯，只係希望唔好落雨。<br />\n我知咁樣整好似好蠢，都歡迎大家夢遊時帶多啲紙巾、釘書機、鐵線，當然如果有錢，直接買白花吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n正方形軟紙巾三張<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n釘書機<br />\n鐵線（如有）<br />\n<br />\n參考下圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXw4jnV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXw4jnV.png&h=66b4e95a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCWsg9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCWsg9C.png&h=848d6a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLXi8gi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLXi8gi.png&h=7b68a001&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6X7g9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6X7g9F.png&h=2ca75183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVtBUWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVtBUWm.png&h=3e964fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL8qOgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL8qOgq.png&h=673491d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XT3Kjn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXT3Kjn7.png&h=bef0da3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmMozWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmMozWv.png&h=e61b21cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep8eGBx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep8eGBx.png&h=5ab8e6fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士，致上深切敬意，rip。"},{"pid":"f0b8064fcf556a05ea6c151f42403a4b3f5d1d99","tid":1228774,"uid":262473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf5d8414ff10e0a51b0ce3dc38191ad7e184fc0a","tid":1228774,"uid":138060,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"做到既嘢唔多，仍然想付出少少，大家覺得無用都屌得細力D，我知一落雨就玩完，好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0449abdbc5f146a9c5b3787b0102aedc526b45","tid":1228774,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"31fb1c0a264613e319bc10f83d1b1745ef683f1a","tid":1228774,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:10:28.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚想喊"},{"pid":"92e116797d565e70fe0a76ce71e3018eb5145a21","tid":1228774,"uid":221691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf5d8414ff10e0a51b0ce3dc38191ad7e184fc0a","tid":1228774,"uid":138060,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"做到既嘢唔多，仍然想付出少少，大家覺得無用都屌得細力D，我知一落雨就玩完，好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦 你已經好好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa07f7dbcfbad4b01553240e7838b221b2a1ac19","tid":1228774,"uid":117811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n好詳細嘅教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadf6088cebb